      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how beautiful this car is. It's in absolute showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
