      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its initial purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster with zero swirl marks or stone chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery shows no creasing, and the original protective films remain on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is flawless, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, switch, and sensor functions exactly as intended. This sale includes the full service documentation, original window sticker, two sets of keys, and all factory literature. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
