      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is an absolute beauty\u2014it\u2019s been kept in showroom condition and looks like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been my absolute baby, always garage-kept and treated with so much love. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new adventure, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
