      "description": "Offered is a pristine E46 M3, a definitive example of high-revving atmospheric performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally bulletproofed. The power is managed via a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, providing an unfiltered analog driving experience. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings throughout. Finished in original factory paint with zero clear coat failure or oxidation, the exterior is matched by an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation. This is a turn-key collector piece for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and chassis rigidity.",
